Sentencas: Ultrasonic mist pyrolysis was applied to electrode preparation for a solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) reactor.

Sentencas: The effect of spray times for periodic operation was investigated.

Sentencas: Different anode catalyst structures were obtained by varying the spray time.
Titulo: Preparation of electrode catalyst for SOFC reactor by ultrasonic mist pyrolysis - Effect of spray time

Sentencas: These structures strongly affected the reactivity of oxidative coupling of methane.
